Observation-only: state_change (with detach reason), completion
(elapsed_ms since UNATTACHED), state_skip (Case B). No behavior change.

Detach reasons: manager_reset | hw_status_check1 | hw_status_report

Signed-off-by: snd-repair phase6 <snd-repair@local>
---
 drivers/soundwire/bus.c | 83 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 83 insertions(+)

--- a/drivers/soundwire/bus.c	2026-07-10 02:04:11.501173398 +0200
+++ b/drivers/soundwire/bus.c
@@ -3,6 +3,7 @@
 
 #include <linux/acpi.h>
 #include <linux/delay.h>
